        "title": "What&#39;s the best way to let a JSF view generate a response to a non-jsf request?",
        "body": "<p>I have a servlet which is in the same web application as the JSF servlet.\nHow do I replace (rather than redirect) the servlet response with the JSF response? <\/p>\n",
