            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1308222205,
            "creation_date": 1306260334,
            "body": "<p>I recommend using <a href=\"http://urlrewritefilter.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/src/doc/manual/3.2/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">urlrewritefilter<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n<p>Simple<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>    &lt;rule&gt;\n        &lt;from&gt;^/my/servlet/uri&lt;/from&gt;\n        &lt;to&gt;/jsfpage.jsf&lt;/to&gt;\n    &lt;/rule&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>should be enough.<\/p>\n",
